sequenceDiagram
    actor DE as 数据工程师
    actor Ann as 标注员
    actor Rev as 审核员
    participant API as API Gateway<br/>(Golang)
    participant TaskSvc as Task Service<br/>(Python)
    participant AnnoTool as 标注工具<br/>(React Frontend)
    participant StreamSvc as 数据流服务<br/>(Golang)
    participant ObjStore as 对象存储
    participant MetaDB as 元数据 DB

    DE->>API: POST /tasks {type, episode_ids,<br/>time_ranges, guideline, deadline}
    API->>TaskSvc: 创建 AnnotationTask
    TaskSvc->>MetaDB: 写入 Task (status=CREATED)
    API-->>DE: {task_id}

    DE->>API: POST /tasks/{id}/assign {user_id}
    API->>TaskSvc: 分配任务
    TaskSvc->>MetaDB: Task status=ASSIGNED
    TaskSvc-->>Ann: 通知: 新任务已分配

    Ann->>AnnoTool: 打开任务
    AnnoTool->>API: GET /tasks/{id}/data-token
    API->>StreamSvc: 生成时限访问令牌<br/>(含 episode_id + time_range)
    API-->>AnnoTool: {stream_token, expires_in}

    AnnoTool->>StreamSvc: 流式请求指定时间段数据<br/>GET /stream/{episode_id}?t=0-30s
    StreamSvc->>ObjStore: 按时间范围读取 MCAP 切片
    StreamSvc-->>AnnoTool: 流式返回帧数据\n(Camera/LiDAR/IMU 同步)

    loop 标注循环
        Ann->>AnnoTool: 绘制标注 (框/关键点/时序标记)
        AnnoTool->>API: POST /annotations/draft (自动保存)
        API->>MetaDB: 保存草稿
    end

    Ann->>AnnoTool: 提交标注
    AnnoTool->>API: POST /annotations/submit {task_id, labels}
    API->>TaskSvc: 更新 Task status=SUBMITTED
    API->>MetaDB: 写入 Annotation (status=SUBMITTED)
    API-->>Ann: 200 OK

    Rev->>API: GET /tasks?status=submitted
    API-->>Rev: [task list]
    Rev->>AnnoTool: 审核模式查看标注
    AnnoTool->>StreamSvc: 同上, 叠加标注图层显示

    alt 审核通过
        Rev->>API: POST /tasks/{id}/approve
        API->>TaskSvc: Task status=APPROVED
        API->>MetaDB: Annotation status=APPROVED
        TaskSvc-->>DE: 事件: AnnotationApproved
    else 审核驳回
        Rev->>API: POST /tasks/{id}/reject {comment}
        API->>TaskSvc: Task status=REJECTED
        TaskSvc-->>Ann: 通知: 任务被驳回 + 反馈
    end
